00032     Selector_List* ss = 0;

00035       if (s->length() == 0) {
00036           Complex_Selector* comb = static_cast<Complex_Selector*>(parent->perform(this));
00037           if (parent->has_line_feed()) comb->has_line_feed(true);

00042         for (size_t j = 0, L = s->length(); j < L; ++j) {

00044           Complex_Selector* comb = static_cast<Complex_Selector*>((*s)[j]->perform(this));

00048         }

00050     }

00093   Selector* Contextualize::operator()(Compound_Selector* s)
00094   {
00095     To_String to_string(&ctx);
00096     if (placeholder && extender && s->perform(&to_string) == placeholder->perform(&to_string)) {
00097       return extender;
00098     }
00099     Compound_Selector* ss = new (ctx.mem) Compound_Selector(s->pstate(), s->length());
00100     ss->last_block(s->last_block());
00101     ss->media_block(s->media_block());
00102     ss->has_line_break(s->has_line_break());
00103     for (size_t i = 0, L = s->length(); i < L; ++i) {
00104       Simple_Selector* simp = static_cast<Simple_Selector*>((*s)[i]->perform(this));
00105       if (simp) *ss << simp;
00106     }
00107     return ss->length() ? ss : 0;
